                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/2018-06-26/debates/0BB7D5AB-0F71-4C6E-9748-68775E1C66D5/HaulagePermitsAndTrailerRegistrationBill(Lords)"><u>Vol. 643 Col. 838</u></a> </p>
                </th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <th>
                  <p>Third Reading </p>
                </th>
                <th>
                  <p>26 June 2018</p>
